{"tid":880051,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"（電腦終於唔洗閂機）大陸廠商改用 Snapdragon 835 製作無風扇靜音筆電","createTime":"2018-10-28T12:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T05:57:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"13eac6cb690fbb1ef36978791b85ef56289c6225","tid":880051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:57:07.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n<br />\n以往有不少大陸的 ODM 電腦生產商，開發和生產俗稱「白牌」的筆電，有些品牌會向大陸生產商訂購，再以貼牌方式變成自家產品再在市場銷售。部份廠商則會將這些白牌筆電直接在市場推出，由於沒有品牌在背後為產品增值，售價通常會比較大眾化。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/M2YsjrWMOFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM2YsjrWMOFw&d=Hniuo78pBfamqklFWhud8v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=08721d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M2YsjrWMOFw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前在香港舉行的 2018 環球資源電子展，就有中國 ODM 電腦生產商微步（Weibu）帶同白牌筆電參展，通常這樣十分常見，但吸引外國傳媒目光的卻是該白牌筆電使用 Qualcomm 處理器。微步爲白牌筆電選用了具有電池續航力較長賣點的 Snapdragon 835 處理器。去年有不少著名電腦品牌，例如聯想（Lenovo）都宣佈會推出 Snapdragon 835 筆電。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n微步的白牌筆電採用 Snapdragon 835 處理器，配搭 4GB RAM 和 64GB 儲存，配備 13.3 吋全高清 1,920 x 1,080 解像度 IPS 屏幕、5,000mAh 容量電池、1MP 像素 Webcam、USB-C 接口、3.5mm 耳機輸出和 802.11ac Wi-Fi。雖然著名大廠今年都已經改用效能更強的第二代 Snapdragon 850 處理器，不過微步的人員表示，使用 Snapdragon 處理器的原因是為了彌補無風扇 Intel Gemini Lake 處理器的不足。"},{"pid":"c9e80e357a163c5e508d9ef071a1fb702385cb1b","tid":880051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/28/weibu-laptop-sd835-china-odm/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2Fweibu-laptop-sd835-china-odm%2Fnotebook%2F&d=Hniuo78pBfamqklFWhud8v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0f120906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/28/weibu-laptop-sd835-china-odm/notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"ea2bc46126987d1bc12bbabfc20a740ecc1d2bc5","tid":880051,"uid":23953,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔用ryzen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b196c8b4fd95bad86a9e56d43f2c0924577fe0ab","tid":880051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea2bc46126987d1bc12bbabfc20a740ecc1d2bc5","tid":880051,"uid":23953,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔用ryzen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:44:18.000Z","msg":"因為平"},{"pid":"46d6be03e80eaad4b0d3a09f69ad3ea70b847fa8","tid":880051,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83af5af6944e18f48fbf3124363bfcbeffc3fd7d","tid":880051,"uid":35752,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"ARM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個chrome都lag到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243bbc1b22e0c99de2d256d2451566f792c1500e","tid":880051,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"83af5af6944e18f48fbf3124363bfcbeffc3fd7d","tid":880051,"uid":35752,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"ARM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個chrome都lag到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"arm手提電腦未用到chrome"},{"pid":"e788ba7a0824c66f42589173fe0c923c2d339acc","tid":880051,"uid":1085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93e8a3a57a13a0580683d207de53883373e1205d","tid":880051,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"家陣唔係有snapdragon 850喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"